abstract: Mustapha Ouanes, a member of the traveling entourage of Saudi Prince Abdul Aziz bin Fahd, is sentenced to 10 years in prison for the rape of a 26-year-old woman who fell asleep in his room at the Plaza Hotel in New York City after a night of barhopping.
lead_paragraph: Mustapha Ouanes, a member of the traveling entourage of Prince Abdul Aziz bin Fahd, faced as much as 25 years on each of the two most serious charges.
